    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/nagaraja-credibility-assessment-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen credibility factors meet or exceed their required gradation levels. The single shortfall in Test conditions (achieved gradation 2 vs. required gradation 3) is acknowledged; however, the assessment team determined that the scope of clinical research application is adequately supported by the available validation evidence under the single-condition ASTM F1717 protocol. Overall credibility is sufficient to support a Medium assurance level decision for the declared intended use.",
